\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line Akademie Konkordia is a new private college and is not yet registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training or accredited to offer higher education programmes by the HEQC. The institution also submitted for accreditation  3 programmes\'3A\line 1. Higher Certificate in Accounting\line 2. Higher Certificate in Community Development\line 3. Diploma in Small Business Management and Entrepreneurship \cell \pard 

